  "description": "MUST activate before writing/editing/deleting any class/id/function. 41 commands. v6.0: Critical bugfixes (7 broken imports fixed: resolve_tauri_ipc, MAX_FILE_SIZE, is_generated_file, scan_binary/tauri_artifacts, time_budget_expired). Preact + @preact/signals detection. Svelte 5 runes ($state/$derived/$effect/$props). Svelte stores (writable/readable/derived). Flexible tauri.conf.json discovery (recursive). Cargo workspace.dependencies parsing. Runtime entry point detection (main/functions in main.rs no longer falsely dead). Debug-leak: console.error/warn no longer flagged as removable. .svelte import tracking in dependents. Monorepo src/ subdir support. 12 langs (JS/TS/Rust/Python/Vue/Svelte/PHP/Blade/C++/Go/Tailwind/HTML), workspace auto-detect.",
